      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SIR MEMPHIS (3) returned last time with a solid second at Dalby over 1100m. Nicely placed to go one better. CLAW MACHINE (1) finished third at Murwillumbah two runs back but was less effective last time over 1400m at Beaudesert, finishing 13 lengths back in eighth. Finds a nice race and can bounce back. TAKARA MOON (4) is a gelding by Wanted out of Mount Maze who is at the races for the first time today. Showed ability with a recent trial placing and can measure up. WHAT DID YOU SAY (5) finished second last start at the first run back from a spell over 1200m at Sunshine Coast when he did his best work late, beaten 6 lengths. Fitter for that run. Placed to advantage and can fill another top-three spot.",
